Job Description
Share
Customer Service, They must greet the customers and respond to their questions and requests in a courteous and helpful way.
Preparing, decorating and displaying food - They prepare food sold in the bakery and must be able to read instructions for food preparation.
Several times each hour they slice, pour, decorate and place food into containers, weigh and attach proper price labels.
Cleaning The Work Area
Experience in decorating 3D cakes (cartoon characters) using decofondant and baking cakes not less than 1 year
