Company Profile
Ayadi is an HR Consultancy that partners with its clients to offer complete recruitment solutions and help them attract, train and retain the manpower they need, and manage the process of moving technical experts onsite as required.
We are objective, fair in selection, and work closely with our clients to determine exact human resource needs before starting the sourcing and matching process. We help mobilize human resource and technical assets on site within agreed time frames to ensure we fit
client's manpower requirements.
